```
dev/active/[task-name]/
├── [task-name]-plan.md     # Approved plan
├── [task-name]-context.md  # Key decisions
└── [task-name]-tasks.md    # Checklist
```

**Workflow**: `/dev-docs` -> implement -> `/update-dev-docs` -> `/compact`

